<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#002</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Redirection configuration endpoints&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>To be confirmed with the Account Squad Solution designers whether new W=
ASH endpoint will be required or existing WASH endpoint to be reused.</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>AccountLinks will be included as part of the consolidatedView in w1c ar=
rangement. Since its existing payload no change is expected for CAP / EXP A=
PI.</li>
</ul>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M065011" =
href=3D"/display/~M065011" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1301392520" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Sailendra Meka</a> <a class=
=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M059852" href=3D"/di=
splay/~M059852" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1212885730" data-linked-resource=
-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"http=
s://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Zane Zuo</a></p>
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M062050" =
href=3D"/display/~M062050" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1515690289" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Andrew Suduk</a> &nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Closed</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#003</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Data masking for alternate accounts</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li style=3D"list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>BCM has mandated that account numbers not entitled to the calling user =
(in the case of redirection/alternate accounts are set up) must not be full=
y displayed to prevent data exposure.</li>
<li>Partial masking (as per Web Application masking guideline from Ben Lim)=
 ensures compliance with BCM=E2=80=99s data security expectations while mai=
ntaining usability for identification purposes.</li>
</ul><p><strong>Masking Rule:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>As per recommendation from ISG, we should display only the <strong>last=
 3 digits for Westpac accounts</strong> and <strong>last 4 digits for St. G=
eorge accounts:</strong>&nbsp;all preceding digits must be replaced with ma=
sking characters (e.g.,&nbsp;<code>XXXXXX123</code>).</li>
<li>No full account number should be exposed in any customer-facing interfa=
ce or API response.</li>
</ul></li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"F060210" =
href=3D"/display/~F060210" data-linked-resource-id=3D"14718653" data-linked=
-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-ur=
l=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Dipti Mistry</a> <a class=3D"co=
nfluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M044638" href=3D"/display/=
~M044638" data-linked-resource-id=3D"42205679" data-linked-resource-version=
=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D"https://conf=
luence.srv.westpac.com.au">Raj Vaishya</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Closed</td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#004</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Deferral of redirection&nbsp;</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>The redirection feature is descoped from the <strong>May 2026 </strong>=
and will be brought forward to <strong>Aug 2026</strong>.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M043727" hre=
f=3D"/display/~M043727" data-linked-resource-id=3D"7256421" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=3D=
"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ben Macaulay</a>&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Closed</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#005</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Inclusion of Line Fee only&nbsp;</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>For <strong>May 2026</strong>, the team will deliver <strong>one fee ty=
pe only</strong>: the <strong>Line Fee for Arranged Overdrafts</strong>, as=
 an end-to-end capability.</li>
<li>The other two fees =E2=80=94 <strong>Unused Limit Fee for Arranged Over=
drafts</strong> and <strong>Line Fee for IDOL</strong> =E2=80=94 will be de=
livered later in the MMP phase, after 10x provides enhancements to support =
multiple fee types.</li>
<li>The goal is to <strong>simplify the May 2026 solution</strong> by remov=
ing the need to differentiate between various fee types.</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"M043727" =
href=3D"/display/~M043727" data-linked-resource-id=3D"7256421" data-linked-=
resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-url=
=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Ben Macaulay</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Closed</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
#006</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Non=E2=80=91financial transactions are NOT in scope for the August delivery=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><br></p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: square;">
<li>As informed by <a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-usern=
ame=3D"F072612" href=3D"/display/~F072612" data-linked-resource-id=3D"12597=
6272" data-linked-resource-version=3D"2" data-linked-resource-type=3D"useri=
nfo" data-base-url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Andrea For</a>=
 , non=E2=80=91financial transactions are NOT in scope for August, it is de=
pendent on a future 10x uplift, which has not yet occurred. This dependency=
 makes August delivery not feasible.</li>
</ul>
<p><br></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" data-username=3D"F080324" =
href=3D"/display/~F080324" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1212876218" data-link=
ed-resource-version=3D"3" data-linked-resource-type=3D"userinfo" data-base-=
url=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au">Aizhan Tulemis</a>&nbsp;</p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Closed</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
